 the `EmailTask` coverage path so the `UUMailer` reflective instantiation can actually be reached.\n\nChanges made:\n\n- Added dedicated test:\n  - `tests/src/ant/ant/1.6/src/test/java/ant/ant/EmailTaskTest.java`\n\n- Added legacy JDK compatibility stub needed for Ant 1.6 `UUMailer` linkage on modern JDKs:\n  - `tests/src/ant/ant/1.6/src/legacyBase64/java/sun/misc/UUEncoder.java`\n\n- Included the legacy compiled classes in the test output/runtime classpath:\n  - `tests/src/ant/ant/1.6/build.gradle`\n\nThe test now configures `EmailTask` with `EmailTask.UU`, calls `execute()` through the public API, and expects execution to pass the reflective `UUMailer` `newInstance()` call before failing at normal Ant validation with `\"A from element is required\"`.\n\nI did not run tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0372bc1e636ebc4c0169f58655da688196b8870e0dc1fad299\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 874, "output": 838, "cacheRead": 51712, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 53424, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777698377614, "responseId": "resp_0372bc1e636ebc4c0169f5864a32508196bb0c056c0f179cb1"}}
